      "content": "i was looking at the street maps for dc today and theres something weird going on with the way the roads connect... it doesnt feel random. like when u look at the main avenues and how they intersect with the monuments, it looks almost intentional. like its shaped like a specific symbol or something. have u ever looked into the urban planning of dc? it feels like there is a hidden geometry there.",
